opengraph.title: Microsoft founder Bill Gates shows vacci | Renegade Tribune
opengraph.description: Microsoft founder Bill Gates shows vaccine during a press conference following his speech at the World Health Assembly to make a push for vaccine programmes, on May 17, 2011 in Geneva. Gates has called on African countries to work harder to get life-saving vaccines to children, as their sluggishness could derail efforts to save millions of lives and stamp out deadly diseases.  AFP PHOTO / FABRICE COFFRINI (Photo credit should read FABRICE COFFRINI/AFP/Getty Images)
